                                <p id="pet-description" class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                                    Cats are independent yet affectionate companions that make wonderful pets for various living situations. 
                                    They are known for their agility, curiosity, and playful nature. Cats are generally low-maintenance 
                                    compared to dogs but still require regular care and attention.
                                </p>
