                                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">Care Requirements</h3>
                                <ul id="care-requirements" class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                                    <li>Provide a balanced, high-protein diet specifically formulated for cats</li>
                                    <li>Ensure access to fresh water at all times</li>
                                    <li>Regular veterinary check-ups and vaccinations</li>
                                    <li>Daily play sessions to stimulate physical and mental health</li>
                                    <li>Regular grooming to maintain healthy coat and skin</li>
                                    <li>Provide a clean litter box in a quiet location</li>
                                </ul>
