                                    <li>Independent nature but can form strong bonds with owners</li>
                                    <li>Territorial behavior, may mark their space</li>
                                    <li>Natural hunters, may exhibit play aggression</li>
                                    <li>Need for vertical spaces to climb and perch</li>
                                    <li>Communication through vocalizations, body language, and scent marking</li>
